  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Risk Management Office (RMO) - Phase III</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project objective is to enable DFID Nepal programmes to work safely and effectively during Nepal&#x2019;s volatile political and ongoing post-conflict transition by providing professional risk management support. The RMO has played an important role in assisting DFID and GIZ programmes and partners to operate safely and effectively in Nepal&apos;s difficult post-conflict environment. RMO&apos;s political updates collated from field helps to manage operational and delivery risks through extensive field network and their expertise in risk management. The RMO has been identified as a best practice in Internal Audit reports recognising this risk management practice as an innovative approach.</narrative>
  </description>
